# Docker build context filter for hexa-lang.
# The runner image only needs:
#   - build/hexa_linux_<arch>           (CLI dispatcher, arm64 + x86_64)
#   - build/hexa_interp_linux_<arch>    (stage0/interp, arm64 + x86_64)
# Everything else just bloats the upload to the buildx daemon.

# Default: ignore everything…
*

# …then re-include the precise paths the Dockerfile COPY'es.
!build/hexa_linux_arm64
!build/hexa_linux_x86_64
!build/hexa_interp_linux_arm64
!build/hexa_interp_linux_x86_64
!docker/

# Keep .git out — multi-MB and never needed by the runner image.
.git/
